reviewText: Barbara Bonney is phenomenal.  The Freiburg Cathedral is beautiful!
Wonderful concert, great for any season of the year.
A very nice Christmas concert, on which one barely notices the missing subtitles. I just can't wait until Holiday season to hear it.

Barbara Bonney is outstanding singing Hndel!
A "must-see/hear".
All music is good but Barbara is breathtakingly good! Beautiful filming as well!
